<p>
  <span class="nym">Pleasant</span>
  <span class="gen">f.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>placens</i>, <i>placentia</i> 'pleasing, satisfying, giving pleasure'.
</span>
  
</p>
  
  


